Frustrating though it is to admit, we have drawn a blank on your query. No
one we have contacted has heard of any Rule of Three. This includes the
Department of Trade and Industry and several senior representatives of the
investment and banking world. Our only suggestion is that your acquaintance
returns to his lending bank for further clarification. (Reply by Murray
Johnstone Ltd).
